name: B.Happy BIT.SHES (SHINE)
description: This limited edition of NFTs, by artist Christina Strok, is part of our first official fundraiser. They have our rarest shining “B.” mark reserved for those seven awesome and special supporters who love what we do and want to support our mission of ART + BLOCKCHAIN + INCLUSION.  Proceeds benefit BIT.SHES ongoing costs, growth, and charitable initiatives. Thanks for your support and enjoy!  See bitshes.com for more.
